sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Activity Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant FS as File Storage
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update activity page
    UI->>LW: mount(activity?)
    LW->>DB: Load activity (if existing) + options (types, campus, staff, status)
    DB-->>LW: Existing data and option lists
    LW-->>UI: Render activity form

    User->>UI: Upload/replace attachment
    UI->>LW: updatedAttachment() / uploadAttachment()
    LW->>FS: Store file (delete old if needed)
    FS-->>LW: File path/filename
    LW-->>UI: Upload success or error toast

    User->>UI: Save activity
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update activity
    LW->>FS: Cleanup replaced file if needed
    DB-->>LW: Persisted activity
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + redirect/list update
